*FIO (from epel)*

* *

This will run a random read test with a 4GB file

fio --randrepeat=1 --ioengine=libaio --direct=1 --gtod\_reduce=1
--name=test --filename=test --bs=4k --iodepth=64 --size=4G
--readwrite=randread

This will run a random write test with a 4GB file

fio --randrepeat=1 --ioengine=libaio --direct=1 --gtod\_reduce=1
--name=test --filename=test --bs=4k --iodepth=64 --size=4G
--readwrite=randwrite

*DD*

dd of=/dev/null if=/home/testfile

*Iotop*

install from epel 

iotop --only - this only shows things actually using I/O
